                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts339" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts340">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>waḷḷa ṣiḥīḥ, daḥḥiǧ! rāyiḥ gāyil l-umm-u gāyil: yuṃṃa! abū-y ǧāyib ḥurma? gāyle: hā? hū ǧāyib ḥurma?</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
