                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>čān aṣīḥ-l-u b-ad-dār hāḏi, waḷḷāhi yā Maryam, gitt: al-ḥurma hāḏi mhabūle, raddid-he! </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
