                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>al-ḥurma in-he mhabūle, gilit: raddid-he! gāḷ: ᵊšnōn arūḥ āni araddid-he? gitt: raddid-he!</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
