                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>čān tugḏ̣ub iḥne ǧaʕad-ᵊnʕammir bēt. al-bēt aǧ ǧāʕde āni bī-´ ḏāk, čān al-ḥurma tiǧi w ttidaʕbal </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
